N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7433.2 - Definitions

State Regulations

As used in this Part, the terms youth division aide and
youth counselor shall mean secure facility staff whose primary duties and
responsibilities shall include, but are not limited to: (a) resident observation; (b) resident management; and
(c) resident supervision. Notes
